# Plan Management

- ALWAYS store implementation plans in `.cursor/plans/`.
- ALWAYS prefix plan filenames with the creation date in `YYYY-MM-DD-` format (e.g., `2026-04-12-my-feature.plan.md`).
- If `.cursor/plans/` directory missing, create it.
- Use `CreatePlan` tool normally, then rename/move result to match this convention.
